&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;College degree or relevant equivalent of professional experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 2 years of related work experience&lt;/li&gt;
