&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;At Real Result and within projects for clients like Victoria Trading, you will focus on the core questions of purchasing: What does the purchasing assignment entail and what requirements must a supplier meet? Why is collaboration with this supplier interesting and what challenge does it offer our clients?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;You will not work with standard dea

