&lt;p&gt;Buyers Edge Platform stands at the forefront of revolutionizing the foodservice industry through technology, purchasing power, and partnerships. We are dedicated to empowering stakeholders across the entire foodservice ecosystem — operators, distributors, and manufacturers — with efficiency and unprecedented visibility. With a diverse portfolio of brands spanning procurement, supply chain, and SaaS solutions, our mission is clear: to reduce costs, streamline the foodservice supply chain, and propel the industry from manual to automated.&lt;/p&gt;
